Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.project

Class Project

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.project.Project
public class Project extends Object
Contains an ISrotedList of CategoryLog s, the AllTasksLog, and operations to manipulate these logs.
Author:
Diya Patel, Jayani Sivakumar

    • addCategoryLog

      public void addCategoryLog(String categoryName)
      Creates a CategoryLog and adds it to the categories in sorted order. The currentLog is updated to the new CategoryLog and isChanged is updated to true.
      Parameters:
      categoryName - the name to add to the categories
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if parameter is null or an empty string or if it matches ALL_TASKS_NAME or there is a duplicate of the existing name

    • getCategoryNames

      public String[] getCategoryNames()
      returns a list of category names. The "All Tasks" log is always listed first.
      Returns:
      names a list of category names

    • setCurrentTaskLog

      public void setCurrentTaskLog(String logName)
      sets the currentLog to the AbstractTaskLog with the given name. If a CategoryLog with that name is not found then the currentLog is set to the allTasksLog.
      Parameters:
      logName - the name to set the currentLog to

    • getCurrentLog

      public AbstractTaskLog getCurrentLog()
      returns the currentLog in the form of a AbstractTaskLog
      Returns:
      log the currentLog

    • editCategoryLogName

      public void editCategoryLogName(String categoryName)
      edits the name of the category
      Parameters:
      categoryName - the name of the category to edit
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the parameter is null or empty String or is a duplicate of another CategoryLog or if the currentLog is an AllTasksLog

    • removeCategoryLog

      public void removeCategoryLog()
      currentLog is removed and then set to the allTasksLog any tasks from the log are removed from AllTasksLog and name is removed
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the currentLog is an AllTasksLog

    • addTask

      public void addTask(Task t)
      adds a task directly to a CategoryLog, currentLog can only be a CategoryLog to add task
      Parameters:
      t - task to add to a CategoryLog

    • editTask

      public void editTask(int idx, String taskName, int taskDuration, String taskDetails)
      updates the fields of the Task at the index given
      Parameters:
      idx - the index of the task to edit
      taskName - the new name of the task
      taskDuration - the new duration of the task
      taskDetails - the new details of the task

    • removeTask

      public void removeTask(int idx)
      removes the task at the index from both CategoryLog and AllTasksLog
      Parameters:
      idx - the task to remove at that index

    • getMostRecentTasks

      public String[][] getMostRecentTasks()
      returns a 2D string array with the last logged item in each categoryLog if there is no logged tasks the title is none for that task and duration is a empty string
      Returns:
      recentTasks a 2D String array with the most recently logged task for each CategoryLog
